metadata.title: Charles-Hubert, Paris Women's 6960-G Premium Collection Analog Display Japanese Quartz Brown Watch
features: Stainless steel case with genuine leather band
description: Since 1990, Charles-Hubert Pans has been a major influence in the United States watch industry. By including both retro and contemporary designs in its line, Charles-Hubert Paris has established a large and loyal following. With its unprecedented Lifetime Warranties, exceptional quality standards and affordable pricing, the future looks very bright for Charles-Hubert Paris.

This classic designed Charles-Hubert Paris watch features stainless steel case, genuine leather band, silver dial with Roman numerals. This watch comes with Japanese Quartz movement, lifetime warranty against manufacturing defects, 30 m (99 ft.) water-resistant and deluxe paper gift box.
